## Display a prompt before each input line
This was done, and it displays the directory of the user. It also updates after using CD.

## Implement a built-in cd command to change directories
This was done and everything works fine. This also updates the prompt before each input line. This is not togglable due to difficulties of introducing
#if flags in the lexer and parser.

